00:17:23.160 --> 00:17:24.280
SPEAKER 1: A doog--

00:17:24.280 --> 00:17:25.756
yeah, our Dooglers here.

00:17:25.756 --> 00:17:27.089
SHANTHI SEKARAN: Yeah, Dooglers.

00:17:27.089 --> 00:17:27.681
Yeah, yeah.

00:17:27.681 --> 00:17:29.430
SPEAKER 1: This is why
I appreciated this,

00:17:29.430 --> 00:17:30.660
because I knew that you
